  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nWhen no `--p2p-private-key-file` option is supplied Teku generates a random KeyPair for NodeID every launch \r\nIt would be more convenient if the private key generated on the first run is persisted and used on subsequent runs when `--p2p-private-key-file` is not set explicitly. \r\n",
